Create Progress Bars Demo
Feature overview:
1.Multiple bars
2.One set of controls that can control each bar on the fly
3.Can't go under 0
4.Can go over 100, but limit the bar itself and change its colour
5.Display usage amount, centred
6.Animate the bar change
7.Linear gradient for the bar
8.Responsive solution: testing it on mobile, tablet, etc. Getting it working nicely.